t-size:12pt"> SMEs and public employers</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">. A</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">ll </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">are </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">based in </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Brussels</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:200%; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">James Higgins</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">: My name is James Higgins. I am the policy officer for employment at the European Youth Forum. The European Youth Forum is the European network of national youth councils and international non-governmental youth organisations, so we represent youth right across the Council of Europe.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:200%; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">The Chairman:</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> The Council of Europe</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">,</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt"> not just the EU</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">? S</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">o you have 40 member states instead of 28?</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:200%; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">James Higgins</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">: Yes. I think we go right the way to </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">Azerbaijan</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size